# Daggerforged Licensing

Daggerforged is a fan-created conversion project combining content from two sources, each with its own license.

## Daggerheart Content

This project includes materials derived from the Daggerheart System Reference Document 1.0, © Critical Role, LLC, used under the terms of the Darrington Press Community Gaming License (DPCGL).

Daggerheart and all related marks are trademarks of Critical Role, LLC and used with permission. This project is not affiliated with, endorsed, or sponsored by Critical Role or Darrington Press.

For full license terms, see: https://www.daggerheart.com/

## Ironsworn / Starforged / Sundered Isles Content

This project references mechanics and terminology from Ironsworn, Starforged, and Sundered Isles by Shawn Tomkin, licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0).

This project is not affiliated with, endorsed, or sponsored by Shawn Tomkin.

For more information: https://www.ironswornrpg.com/

## Daggerforged Original Content

Any original content created for Daggerforged (conversion text, design decisions, organizational structure) is released under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0).

You are free to:
- Share — copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format
- Adapt — remix, transform, and build upon the material for any purpose, even commercially

Under the following terms:
- Attribution — You must give appropriate credit, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made.

## Required Attribution

If you use or adapt Daggerforged content, please include:

1. Credit to Critical Role, LLC for Daggerheart content
2. Credit to Shawn Tomkin for Ironsworn/Starforged/Sundered Isles content
3. A note that Daggerforged is a fan project, not an official product

## No Warranty

This project is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. Use at your own risk.
